28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Noto Serif&#39;, serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28.0007px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 28px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Noto Serif&#39;, serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28.0007px; white-space: normal;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><h3 style=\"clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 28px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.1667;\"><strong>2、</strong><strong><a href=\"{#ZC_BLOG_HOST#}archives/1079\" target=\"_blank\" data-mce-href=\"{#ZC_BLOG_HOST#}archives/1079\" style=\"border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration: none;\">北仑口腔医院官方网站及其预约系统（BLKQ）</a></strong><br/></h3></li></ul><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Noto Serif&#39;, serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28.0007px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 北仑口腔官方网站及其预约系统是宁波市北仑区口腔医院的一个外包项目，历史2个月，现已上线且运行良好</div><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Noto Serif&#39;, serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28.0007px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 28px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Noto Serif&#39;, serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28.0007px; white-space: normal;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><h3 style=\"clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 28px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.1667;\"><strong>1、<a href=\"{#ZC_BLOG_HOST#}archives/330\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"bookmark\" data-mce-href=\"{#ZC_BLOG_HOST#}archives/330\" style=\"border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration: none;\">互联网特定序号文件下载器v1.0</a></strong><br/></h3></li></ul><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Noto Serif&#39;, serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28.0007px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 能够批量下载互联网中具有特定需要的资源（该资源之前在sina博客发