font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#494949\"><br/> </span><a href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=68b4ec9b0101ctm0&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/68b4ec9bzx6Coh0hpXC2c\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#526673;text-underline:none\"><img src=\"{#ZC_BLOG_HOST#}zb_users/upload/2016/04/201604101460272759103534.png\" title=\"正在上传...\" alt=\"blob.png\"/></span></a><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#494949\"><br/> </span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#494949\">远观沙漠，为这边的草原担忧。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 5px;line-height: 21px;word-wrap: normal;background: rgb(246, 246, 246)\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#494949\">&nbsp;</span><wbr/></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 5px;line-height: 21px;word-wrap: normal;background: rgb(246, 246, 246)\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#494949\"><br/> </span><a href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=68b4ec9b0101ctm0&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/68b4ec9bzx6Coh0om6U24\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#526673;text-underline:none\"><img src=\"{#ZC_BLOG_HOST#}zb_users/upload/2016/04/201604101460272764851857.png\" title=\"正在上传...\" alt=\"blob.png\"/></span></a><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#494949\"><br/> </span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#494949\">和小伙伴们一起的合影，其实不止这些小伙伴的后面还有的。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 5px;line-height: 21px;word-wrap: normal;background: rgb(246, 246, 246)\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#494949\">&nbsp;</span><wbr/></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 5px;line-height: 21px;word-wrap: normal;background: rgb(246, 246, 246)\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#494949\"><br/> </span><a href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=68b4ec9b0101ctm0&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/68b4ec9bzx6Coh0Jarv49\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#526673;text-underline:none\"><img src=\"{#ZC_BLOG_HOST#}zb_users/upload/2016/04/201604101460272771946785.png\" title=\"正在上传...\" alt=\"blob.png\"/></span></a><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#494949\"><br/> <br/> </span><a href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=68b4ec9b0101ctm0&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/68b4ec9bzx6Coh1sK6A60\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#526673;text-underline:none\"><img src=\"{#ZC_BLOG_HOST#}zb_users/upload/2016/04/201604101460272786104920.png\" title=\"正在上传...\" alt=\"blob.png\"/></span></a><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#494949\"><br/> </span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#494949\">沙漠全景！</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 5px;line-height: 21px;word-wrap: normal;background: rgb(246, 246, 246)\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#494949\"><br/> </span><a href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=68b4ec9b0101ctm0&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/68b4ec9bzx6Coh21DPs0a\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#526673;text-underline:none\"><img src=\"{#ZC_BLOG_HOST#}zb_users/upload/2016/04/201604101460272795126599.png\" title=\"正在上传...\" alt=\"blob.png\"/></span></a><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#494949\"><br/> </span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#494949\">所有的小伙伴都在这里有木有，这应该是到这个时候玩的最开心的一天，来自全国各个地方的人因为兴趣聚集在一起，一起疯狂的玩了一天又匆匆的离开，相聚别离匆匆的在生命中上演，你必须适应它。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 16px;line-height: 21px;word-wrap: normal;background: rgb(246, 246, 246)\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#494949\"><br/> </span><a href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=68b4ec9b0101ctm0&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/68b4ec9bzx6Coh2FxySae\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#526673;text-underline:none\"><img src=\"{#ZC_BLOG_HOST#}zb_users/upload/2016/04/201604101460272799542975.png\" title=\"正在上传...\" alt=\"blob.png\"/></span></a><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#494949\"><br/> </span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#494949\">沙漠的天空真的很不错，相机拍摄效果不好。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 5px;line-height: 21px;word-wrap: normal;background: rgb(246, 246, 246)\"><a href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=68b4ec9b0101ctm0&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/68b4ec9bzx6Coq1Xurz1d\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#526673;text-underline:none\"><img src=\"{#ZC_BLOG_HOST#}zb_users/upload/2016/04/201604101460272805901601.png\" title=\"正在上传...\" alt=\"blob.png\"/></span></a><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#494949\"><br/> </span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#494949\">一望无际的公路，天气不错。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 5px;line-height: 21px;word-wrap: normal;background: rgb(246, 246, 246)\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#494949\">&nbsp;</span><wbr/></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 5px;line-height: 21px;word-wrap: normal;background: rgb(246, 246, 246)\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#494949\"><br/> </span><a href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=68b4ec9b0101ctm0&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/68b4ec9bzx6Coq27OXcc6\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;simsun&#39;,&#39;serif&#39